title: Mamabrum Dolls House with Furniture Set – Large 3-Story Wooden Playhouse with LED Lights – Fully Furnished Dollhouse for Girls – Pretend Play Set for Kids 3+
features: Spacious 3-Story Dollhouse: This beautifully crafted large wooden dollhouse features three levels of play, elegant pastel designs, and multiple rooms for endless imaginative play
Fully Furnished with LED Lighting: Comes with wooden furniture and accessories, including bunk beds, a vanity table, kitchen set, sofa, and more. Built-in LED lights create a magical ambiance
Safe & Durable Construction: Made from sturdy MDF and wood, this house is robust, free from sharp edges, and coated with non-toxic paint, ensuring safe play
Excellent Gift for Girls 3+ Years: Designed to inspire creativity, role-playing, and storytelling, this dollhouse for girls is an ideal gift for birthdays, Christmas, or special occasions
Easy Assembly & Maintenance: With included step-by-step instructions, this big dollhouse is simple to assemble and easy to clean, providing long-lasting fun for kids
description: Giant wooden dollhouse with furniture and LED lighting. Brand: Mamabrum Model: A405 A huge amount of mobile furniture, LED backlight, beautiful pastel colors, this is a dream home for the most demanding dolls. Every girl dreams of being able to play with her dolls in such a beautiful house. No sharp edges, solid construction, totally safe. The set is equipped with LED lighting powered by AA batteries (3 pieces). Batteries not included. The set includes: large wooden house with 3 floors with terrace, bunk bed with bedding, dressing table, ottoman shower cubicle with shower head, toilet seat with opening lid, washbasin with mirror, table and two chairs, kitchen floor lamp with opening cabinets, sofa bench with soft pillow, armchair with soft cushion, staircase with LED lighting, assembly instructions (English language not guaranteed). It is a fantastic addition to the fun. Create magical moments, just like in a real house. The toy will provide long hours of fantastic fun. The house is very easy to clean. Suitable for ages 3 and up. Dimensions: 60 x 30 x 90 cm. Material: Wood, MDF. Accessories: furniture, LED lighting. Self assembly required. Instructions included
